A REFUND ON THAT.

33:01.875 --> 33:04.917
DAD, I KNOW YOU THINK
I'M MAKING A MISTAKE,

33:04.917 --> 33:07.333
BUT IF I AM, IT'S
A MISTAKE I HAVE TO MAKE
FOR MYSELF, ALL RIGHT?

33:07.333 --> 33:09.667
AND I KNOW WHEN YOU
THINK ABOUT THIS,

33:09.667 --> 33:12.458
YOU'RE GONNA REALIZE
I'M ONLY TRYING TO BE
THE KIND OF PERSON

33:12.458 --> 33:13.583
YOU TAUGHT ME TO BE.

33:13.583 --> 33:15.792
I THINK YOU ARE  MAKING
A MISTAKE, DAWSON,

33:15.792 --> 33:17.041
A HUGE MISTAKE,

33:17.041 --> 33:21.750
AND I AM
DISAPPOINTED IN YOU.

33:29.834 --> 33:30.834
BUT NEVER, EVER

33:30.834 --> 33:34.875
FOR A SINGLE SECOND FORGET

33:34.875 --> 33:36.125
THAT I LOVE YOU...

33:38.667 --> 33:41.708
AND I WILL ALWAYS
BE HERE FOR YOU.

33:55.041 --> 33:57.041
MOM?

33:57.041 --> 33:59.333
HE'LL BE FINE.

33:59.333 --> 34:00.542
CALL HIM.

34:00.542 --> 34:01.500
I WILL.

34:01.500 --> 34:03.333
[LILY CRIES]

34:03.333 --> 34:05.041
SHH.

34:48.166 --> 34:49.417
SO...

34:49.417 --> 34:51.041
BREAKING AND ENTERING
A TYPICAL SECOND DATE
FOR YOU?

34:51.041 --> 34:52.083
WE'RE NOT
BREAKING AND ENTERING.

34:52.083 --> 34:54.750
HEY, THE WINDOW
WAS OPEN, RIGHT?

34:54.750 --> 34:57.291
ISN'T THAT JUST
A LITTLE BIT CONVENIENT?

34:57.291 --> 35:00.041
NO, BECAUSE THERE'S
NOTHING IN HERE
WORTH STEALING...

35:00.041 --> 35:00.834
EXCEPT...

35:00.834 --> 35:02.542
A BOSTON BAY
TRADITION.

35:02.542 --> 35:05.458
WHAT, BREAKING INTO
THIS HEALTH CENTER
AND STEALING CONDOMS

35:05.458 --> 35:07.166
IS A BOSTON BAY
TRADITION?

35:07.166 --> 35:09.083
IT'S NOT STEALING.
THEY'RE FREE. SEE?
READ THE SIGN.

35:09.083 --> 35:11.583
"GIFT TO THE CLASS
OF 1990.

35:11.583 --> 35:12.208
HERE'S HOPING
YOU GET LAID."

35:14.250 --> 35:17.375
