THAT THAT SIGN SAYS?

35:17.375 --> 35:17.917
WELL, SOMETHING
LIKE THAT.

35:17.917 --> 35:19.834
I'M PARAPHRASING.

35:19.834 --> 35:21.750
LOOK. I HAVEN'T ACTUALLY
BEEN HERE IN A WHILE.

35:21.750 --> 35:22.792
SO IF WE COULD JUST
GET WHAT WE CAME FOR--

35:22.792 --> 35:25.375
YOU CAN'T READ
THE SIGN, CAN YOU?

35:25.375 --> 35:27.166
OH, COME ON.
WHO COULD READ THAT
FROM HERE?

35:27.166 --> 35:29.291
THAT'S LIKE CHINA
FROM HERE.

35:29.291 --> 35:31.375
"GIFT TO THE CLASS
OF 1990,

35:31.375 --> 35:34.333
IN ANTICIPATION
OF A WORLD WITHOUT AIDS."

35:35.333 --> 35:36.834
I WAS CLOSE.

35:36.834 --> 35:38.166
[CHUCKLES]

35:38.166 --> 35:41.625
YOU ARE TOTALLY
NEARSIGHTED, AREN'T YOU?

35:41.625 --> 35:42.875
I'M NOT NEARSIGHTED.

35:42.875 --> 35:45.041
I JUST--

35:45.041 --> 35:49.083
I JUST CAN'T READ
REALLY TEENY THINGS
FAR AWAY.

35:49.083 --> 35:50.959
LIKE--I DON'T KNOW--

35:50.959 --> 35:52.083
UM, SUBTITLES?

35:52.083 --> 35:53.500
YES. SUBTITLES,
ALL RIGHT?

35:53.500 --> 35:54.792
I HATE SUBTITLES BECAUSE
I CAN'T READ THEM
WITHOUT MY GLASSES.

35:54.792 --> 35:57.333
YOU SATISFIED?

35:57.333 --> 35:59.375
YES.

35:59.375 --> 36:01.792
ACTUALLY, I THINK THAT
THIS LITTLE FIELD TRIP
WAS A GOOD IDEA

36:01.792 --> 36:04.792
BECAUSE NOW I FINALLY
KNOW SOMETHING ABOUT YOU.

36:05.750 --> 36:06.834
WHAT, THAT I'M
NEARSIGHTED?

36:06.834 --> 36:08.750
TRUST ME.

36:08.750 --> 36:10.583
THEY MAKE ME LOOK
LIKE A TOTAL DORK.

36:10.583 --> 36:11.708
YOU ARE  A TOTAL DORK,

36:11.708 --> 36:13.333
A VAIN DORK.

36:14.959 --> 36:16.500
COME HERE AND KISS ME.

36:28.375 --> 36:30.291
Jack: I DON'T WANT
TO BE WANTED JUST TO--

36:30.291 --> 36:31.625
TO FILL
SOME KIND OF QUOTA.

36:31.625 --> 36:35.417
WELL, YOU KNOW
THE REASON WE FIRST
CAME AFTER YOU, JACK,

36:35.417 --> 36:37.000
BUT THE TRUTH IS,

36:37.000 --> 36:38.458
MAN, WE REALLY LIKE YOU.

36:38.458 --> 36:39.959
DON'T BE THROWN
BY THIS QUOTA THING.

36:39.959 --> 36:41.166
YEAH, YOU'RE
FILLING ONE.

36:41.166 --> 36:43.083
I'M FILLING ONE.
