HAS QUALITIES
AND EXPERIENCES

36:45.250 --> 36:46.750
THAT ARE UNIQUE.

36:46.750 --> 36:47.792
THAT'S WHY SIGMAS
KICK BUTT.

36:47.792 --> 36:49.333
YEAH, BUT YOU WANT
A GAY GUY IN THE HOUSE--

36:49.333 --> 36:51.250
YES, WE DO,

36:51.250 --> 36:53.792
BUT YOU'RE
THE ONE WE WANT.

36:55.166 --> 36:57.250
ALL RIGHT, BUT DO YOU
UNDERSTAND THE REALITY

36:57.250 --> 36:59.125
OF WHAT YOU'RE
GONNA GET HERE?

36:59.125 --> 37:01.417
I MEAN, MY BOYFRIEND, TOBEY,
WHEN HE COMES TO VISIT,

37:01.417 --> 37:03.375
I MEAN, HE'S
GONNA BE EATING HERE
AND PARTYING HERE, TOO,

37:03.375 --> 37:04.583
AND IF I LIVE
IN THE HOUSE, YOU KNOW,

37:04.583 --> 37:08.041
HE'S GONNA BE SLEEPING HERE
AND SHOWERING HERE.

37:08.041 --> 37:09.250
JACK...

37:09.250 --> 37:10.667
TOBEY IS WELCOME.

37:10.667 --> 37:12.208
EVEN IF YOU DON'T
LIVE AT THE HOUSE,

37:12.208 --> 37:14.041
IF HE NEEDS
A PLACE TO CRASH,

37:14.041 --> 37:15.542
THIS IS HIS HOME, TOO.

37:15.542 --> 37:17.542
THAT'S WHAT IT MEANS
TO BE A BROTHER.

37:17.542 --> 37:19.375
COOL.

37:19.375 --> 37:20.417
SO WHAT
DO YOU SAY, JACK?

37:25.959 --> 37:28.875
I SAY SIGN ME UP!

37:28.875 --> 37:29.708
WELCOME TO THE HOUSE,
BROTHER.

37:29.708 --> 37:30.333
THANKS, MAN.

37:30.333 --> 37:31.834
Brother: ALL RIGHT!

37:31.834 --> 37:33.917
POLAR BEAR. YEAH!

37:33.917 --> 37:35.708
[ALL CHEERING]

37:35.708 --> 37:36.792
ALL RIGHT!

37:36.792 --> 37:38.333
YEAH!

37:38.333 --> 37:38.834
WHOO!

37:38.834 --> 37:40.417
YEAH!

37:43.834 --> 37:46.083
HEY. I'M DONE.

37:46.083 --> 37:48.917
42 POUNDS OF PEELED
AND SLICED POTATOES.

37:48.917 --> 37:50.500
NOW, MAY I PLEASE
COOK THEM?

37:50.500 --> 37:52.625
QUIET.
OK.

37:52.625 --> 37:54.083
WELL, NOW.

37:54.083 --> 37:56.375
LOOKS LIKE YOU STARTED
GETTING THE HANG OF IT
TOWARD THE END HERE.

37:56.375 --> 37:57.917
THERE'S HOPE FOR YOU.

37:57.917 --> 38:00.542
AH, THANKS.

38:00.542 --> 38:02.041
WHAT ARE YOU DO--

38:02.041 --> 38:03.500
THAT WAS HOURS
OF WORK, MAN!

38:05.750 --> 38:07.917
I DON'T
SERVE POTATO CHIPS
IN MY RESTAURANT.

38:07.917 --> 38:09.417
REALLY?

38:09.417 --> 38:13.333
SO THEN WHY
DID YOU WASTE MY TIME
AND YOUR MONEY

38:13.333 --> 38:14.792
HAVING ME DO THAT?

38:14.792 --> 38:15.125
TRAINING.

38:15.125 --> 38:16.792
AH.

38:16.792 --> 38:18.125
OK. HERE,
WACK JOB.

38:18.125 --> 38:19.125
SLICE.

38:19.125 --> 38:20.041
WHAT IS THAT?

38:20.041 --> 38:21.834
FORGET ABOUT WHAT IT IS.

38:21.834 --> 38:23.500
SLICE IT,
JUST LIKE THE POTATO.

38:27.959 --> 38:29.000
THAT'S NOT BAD.

38:29.000 --> 38:30.458
YOU'RE LEARNING.

38:30.458 --> 38:31.208
NOW WOULD YOU MIND
TELLING ME WHAT THIS
IS ALL ABOUT?

38:31.208 --> 38:35.291
BEHOLD
THE WHITE TRUFFLE--

38:35.291 --> 38:38.500
SO FRESH THAT
YOU CAN ACTUALLY SEE
THE LITTLE HOOF MARKS

38:38.500 --> 38:42.291
FROM THE PIG
THAT DUG IT OUT OF
THE I-TALIAN SOIL.

38:42.291 --> 38:46.250
THESE BABIES GO
FOR $1,200 A POUND.

38:46.250 --> 38:47.959
WHAT?

38:49.125 --> 38:50.875
THAT'S THE MOST RIDICULOUS
THING I'VE EVER HEARD.

38:50.875 --> 38:53.291
NOW, IF I LET
SOME HEADSTRONG KID

38:53.291 --> 38:55.333
GET ANYWHERE NEAR THEM
WITHOUT PROPER TRAINING,

38:55.333 --> 38:59.250
I REALLY WOULD BE
A WACK JOB.

38:59.250 --> 38:59.625
TASTE.

39:06.250 --> 39:07.708
OK. I GET IT.

39:07.708 --> 39:11.375
KAREN HAS MORE
DISCIPLINE
AND MOTIVATION

39:11.375 --> 39:14.375
THAN A SLACK-ASS
LIKE YOU WILL EVER HAVE,

39:14.375 --> 39:17.708
BUT THIS ISN'T
KICK BOXING,

39:17.708 --> 39:20.041
AND THAT'S WHY
I WOULDN'T GIVE HER
YOUR JOB.

39:21.166 --> 39:23.750
HA HA HA!
SHE WANTED MY JOB.

39:23.750 --> 39:24.959
YEAH.

39:24.959 --> 39:27.166
YOU'RE NOT GONNA
PICK THIS UP
THROUGH SHEER WILL.

39:27.166 --> 39:29.333
COOKING IS A CRAFT

39:29.333 --> 39:30.750
WHICH CAN'T BE TAUGHT.

39:30.750 --> 39:32.625
HOWEVER,

39:32.625 --> 39:33.500
IT CAN BE LEARNED.

39:35.000 --> 39:37.041
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

39:37.041 --> 39:39.083
CLEAN UP YOUR STATION.

39:39.083 --> 39:41.917
YOU'RE COOKING
THE TRUFFLE RAVIOLI
TOMORROW.

39:51.041 --> 39:52.500
Dawson: HOW WAS
YOUR WEEKEND?

39:55.041 --> 39:56.166
STRANGE AND UNUSUAL.

39:56.166 --> 39:58.375
HOW ABOUT YOURS?

39:58.375 --> 40:00.750
STRANGE AND UNPLEASANT.

40:00.750 --> 40:02.333
YOU OK?

40:04.041 --> 40:05.083
NOT REALLY.

40:05.083 --> 40:07.375
I ALIENATED MY PARENTS,

40:07.375 --> 40:10.166
AND NOW I FIND MYSELF
ADRIFT IN A SEA
OF UNCERTAINTY.

40:11.458 --> 40:13.375
BUT, HEY, WHAT ELSE
IS NEW, RIGHT?

40:13.375 --> 40:16.625
CAN I DO
SOMETHING TO HELP?

40:16.625 --> 40:20.834
YEAH. YOU CAN TELL ME
THAT I, WITHOUT A DOUBT,
MADE THE RIGHT DECISION

40:20.834 --> 40:23.250
AND THAT THIS DECISION
WILL HAVE NOTHING BUT
POSITIVE REPERCUSSIONS

40:23.250 --> 40:24.834
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE.

40:24.834 --> 40:27.166
DAWSON, I CAN'T DO THAT.

40:28.291 --> 40:29.583
DAMN.

40:30.667 --> 40:32.458
BUT I CAN TELL YOU THIS.

40:32.458 --> 40:35.542
THERE IS NO
RIGHT OR WRONG,

40:35.542 --> 40:37.917
JUST CONSEQUENCES
OF YOUR ACTIONS.

40:40.291 --> 40:42.625
WHAT THE HELL
DOES THAT MEAN?

40:42.625 --> 40:44.708
WELL,
I'M NOT SURE EXACTLY.

40:44.708 --> 40:47.959
MY SOCIOLOGY PROFESSOR
SAID THAT LAST WEEK,

40:47.959 --> 40:49.291
AND I THOUGHT IT
SOUNDED PRETTY PROFOUND
AT THE TIME.

40:49.291 --> 40:50.917
GREAT.

40:50.917 --> 40:52.625
I SHOULD JUST GET
ON A PLANE RIGHT NOW.

40:52.625 --> 40:55.417
WE CAN'T.
WE TRIED THAT ALREADY.

40:55.417 --> 40:57.250
WE CAN'T SEEM TO GET
YOU ON THAT PLANE.

40:57.250 --> 40:59.000
YOU'RE LIKE
DUSTIN HOFFMAN
IN RAIN MAN.

41:03.375 --> 41:06.000
HOW ABOUT
A CUP OF COFFEE?

41:07.250 --> 41:08.375
SURE.

41:08.375 --> 41:09.417
IT'S ABOUT TIME
I GOT ACQUAINTED

41:09.417 --> 41:12.333
WITH THIS CITY
OF YOURS.

41:16.875 --> 41:18.083
SO HOW WAS CAPESIDE?

41:18.083 --> 41:19.667
SAME OLD SAME OLD.

41:19.667 --> 41:22.542
THEY'RE TEARING DOWN
THE NEW RIALTO,

41:22.542 --> 41:25.667
BUILDING, LIKE,
A NEW 16-THEATER
MULTIPLEX OR SOMETHING.

41:25.667 --> 41:26.875
I GUESS IT JUST GOES
TO SHOW YOU.

41:26.875 --> 41:28.792
WHAT?

41:28.792 --> 41:31.250
YOU CAN NEVER
GO HOME AGAIN.

41:36.291 --> 41:41.041
Mitch: ♪ I WANT YOU TO KNOW,
I BELIEVE IN YOUR SONG ♪

41:42.500 --> 41:45.708
♪ THE RHYTHM, THE RHYME,
THE HARMONY ♪

41:48.917 --> 41:51.333
♪ YOU HELPED ME ALONG ♪

41:51.333 --> 41:54.333
♪ MAKIN' ME STRONG ♪

41:54.333 --> 41:57.333
♪ GIVE ME THE BEAT, BOY ♪

41:57.333 --> 41:58.667
OH.

41:58.667 --> 42:00.083
UH...

42:11.291 --> 42:13.333
[BRAKES SCREECH]

42:13.333 --> 42:15.250
[HORN BLARES]
